revisions.description: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
New objects were added to the Juniper-OSPF-MIB juniOspfBasicGroup2.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniOspfAgentV1.name: juniOspfAgentV1
juniOspfAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the OSPF component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the OSPF component was supported in JUNOSe 2.x and 3.x system
        releases.

juniOspfAgentV2.name: juniOspfAgentV2
juniOspfAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the OSPF component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the OSPF component is supported in JUNOSe 4.0 and subsequent system
        releases.
